Blurb::
Parameter for the DR or DRAM MCMC algorithms in MUQ

Description::
Value of parameter 'b' in equation for the scaling scalar 'a_i' in the i-th stage, i=0,1,...,N-1, where N is the number of stages (parameter dr_num_stages).
The equation can be either a_i = b/(i+1) (in case of dr_scale_type = "Linear") or a_i = b/2^i (in case of dr_scale_type = "Power).
Value must be positive.

